                      "fill": "$--text-primary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Welcome to 742 Evergreen Terrace — a stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom single-family home nestled in one of Springfield's most sought-after neighborhoods. Built in 2019, this modern residence offers 3,200 sq ft of thoughtfully designed living space on a generous 0.45-acre lot.",
