                      "fill": "$--text-primary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Step inside to discover an open-concept floor plan featuring a gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a large center island. The spacious living room boasts hardwood floors and a cozy fireplace, perfect for entertaining. The luxurious master suite includes a walk-in closet and spa-inspired en-suite bathroom.",
